name unicode-math
category Package
revision 78251
shortdesc Unicode mathematics support for XeTeX and LuaTeX
longdesc This package provides a comprehensive implementation of unicode
longdesc maths for XeLaTeX and LuaLaTeX. Unicode maths requires an
longdesc OpenType mathematics font, of which there are now a number
longdesc available via CTAN. While backwards compatibility is strived
longdesc for, there are some differences between the legacy mathematical
longdesc definitions in LaTeX and amsmath, and the Unicode mathematics
longdesc definitions. Care should be taken when transitioning from a
longdesc legacy workflow to a Unicode-based one.
depend amsmath
depend fontspec
depend lm-math
depend lualatex-math
